              <span aria-hidden="true">🔍</span> SEO &amp; STRUCTURED DATA
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              Meta titles, descriptions, Open Graph tags for social sharing, Twitter cards,
              canonical URLs, XML sitemap, robots.txt, and JSON-LD schema markup that tells
              Google exactly what your business does, where you are, and how to contact you.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">🔒</span> SECURITY HEADERS
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              SSL/HTTPS encryption, Content Security Policy, X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options,
              Referrer-Policy, and Permissions-Policy headers. These protect your visitors and your
              reputation — and Google rewards secure sites with higher rankings.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">⚡</span> PERFORMANCE OPTIMISATION
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              Image compression and modern formats (WebP/AVIF), lazy loading, minified CSS and
              JavaScript, efficient font loading with preconnect hints, optimised critical rendering
              path, and Cloudflare CDN caching. The result: sub-second load times.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--nebula-purple); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">♿</span> ACCESSIBILITY
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              Semantic HTML structure, ARIA labels, keyboard navigation, sufficient colour contrast,
              alt text on images, and proper heading hierarchy. Your site works for everyone —
              including screen reader users — and meets legal accessibility requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">📨</span> CONTACT FORM BACKEND
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              Server-side form handling with validation, honeypot spam traps, rate limiting,
              and email delivery configuration. Enquiries land in your inbox reliably — not
              in spam — and bots cannot flood you with junk submissions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">📊</span> ANALYTICS &amp; MONITORING
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              Google Analytics or privacy-friendly alternatives configured properly — tracking
              real visitors, not bots. You will know how people find your site, which pages they
              visit, and whether your site is converting visitors into enquiries.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">🗺️</span> SITEMAP &amp; ROBOTS.TXT
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              An XML sitemap tells search engines every page on your site and when it was last updated.
              Robots.txt controls which pages get crawled. Without these, Google is guessing — with them,
              it indexes your site properly.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">🖼️</span> IMAGE OPTIMISATION
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              Every image is compressed, converted to modern formats (WebP/AVIF), correctly sized,
              and lazy-loaded so it only downloads when visible. This alone can cut page load time
              in half compared to unoptimised sites.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--nebula-purple); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">📱</span> RESPONSIVE DESIGN ENGINEERING
