              collapses properly, text stays readable, images resize, and touch targets are large
              enough to tap. Tested across phones, tablets, laptops, and desktops.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span aria-hidden="true">🌐</span> DNS &amp; DOMAIN CONFIGURATION
            </h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
              Domain setup, DNS records, SSL provisioning, email routing (MX records), and redirect
              rules. We handle the full infrastructure so your site works reliably at your custom
              domain from day one — no broken links or certificate warnings.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
